package_info.message: Provided tab and tab group keyboard utilitiy shortcuts and auto hide unfocused tab groups.

TAH_NextTab.message: Focus the right tab, even if it's in a collapsed group.

TAH_PreviousTab.message: Focus the left tab, even if it's in a collapsed group.

TAH_MoveTabRight.message: Move tab right. Might merge into the next group.

TAH_MoveTabLeft.message: Move tab left. Might merge into the previous group.
